Outstanding dive shop and scuba training.  I just finished my scuba certification with George from Inland Divers this morning.  These guys are extremely thorough.  They are affiliated with NAUI and go above and beyond the training requirements to make sure that you're totally comfortable going diving safely.  My wife and I bought our gear at the shop - their prices and products are excellent.  If you're thinking about getting scuba certified I wouldn't recommend going anywhere else.

